CONCEPT: Execution failure
=========================================================

OBJECTIVE

- Understand what "out of gas" means
- See how loops can cause execution failure
- Learn why gas limits exist
- Think like an auditor about DOS risks

---------------------------------------------------------
CORE IDEA
